title: Cheryl fans convinced singer has ALREADY given birth to Liam Payne's baby after calculating due date as being over a week ago
text:
The singer was eight month's pregnant when she posed for L'Oreal's new confidence campaign with a host of other celebrities 
A video has also been released featuring Cheryl and other celebrities including actress Helen Mirren. 
Cheryl, who has her own charity with the Prince’s Trust called Cheryl’s Trust, was not paid for the shoot. 
The former X Factor judge recently announced that she is opening a charity centre for disadvantaged young people in Newcastle. Getty Images - WireImage 7 Cheryl has been dating One Direction star Liam Payne for over a year, and the couple are just days away from welcoming their first child 
Cheryl and 1D star Liam, 23, have been in a relationship for over a year after getting together in late 2015 following Cheryl’s split from ex-husband Jean Bernard Fernandez-Versini . 
Her pregnancy rumours first began in September last year after she appeared in a different L’Oreal campaign sporting an unusually plump face. 
Fans then went into a frenzy when Liam changed his Twitter bio to describe himself as “the luckiest man in the world”. related stories Here's all you need to know about Cheryl's relationship with Liam Payne 'WE'LL ALWAYS BE 1D' One Direction's Liam Payne makes surprise appearance at the BRIT Awards 2017 NOT LONG TO GO! The former Girls Aloud star has kept a relatively low profile throughout her pregnancy and scaled back her work commitments. 
Cheryl filed for divorce from ex-husband Jean-Bernard Fernandez-Versini in January after being married for just 19 months. 
She was previously married to former England footballer Ashley Cole before they divorced in 2010 after six years together. Cheryl unveils enormous baby bump during glamorous new photo shoot
